            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-f09fcd twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 3.  Information about the Project Gutenberg Literary Archive\nFoundation</h4></div>"
