            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-f09fcd twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
