        "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-f09fcd twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-6b4cd0\"><p>The Foundation is committed to complying with the laws regulating\ncharities and charitable donations in all 50 states of the United\nStates.  Compliance requirements are not uniform and it takes a\nconsiderable effort, much paperwork and many fees to meet and keep up\nwith these requirements.  We do not solicit donations in locations\nwhere we have not received written confirmation of compliance.  To\nSEND DONATIONS or determine the status of compliance for any\nparticular state visit https://pglaf.org</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-f09fcd twpub-06a27d3ff0a13d5f-6b4cd0\"><p>While we cannot and do not solicit contributions from states where we\nhave not met the solicitation requirements, we know of no prohibition\nagainst accepting unsolicited donations from donors in such states who\napproach us with offers to donate.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/06a27d3ff0a13d5f/text/000001277": {
